data.description: Welcome home to this charming two bedroom, two bathroom townhome nestled at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. With its own private entrance and patio, this lovely home offers a serene retreat. Step inside to be greeted by an inviting open living room adorned with high ceilings, providing a wonderful sense of space. Perfect for first-time homeowners, this property has incredible potential and only awaits your personal touch. The low HOA fee includes access to fantastic community amenities such as a tennis court, pool, and clubhouse. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
